.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, animation, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | animation | zombie | family |

