3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | helicopter | jet-ski | ship |

